                                                                    &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;i) &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&ensp;<b>Insolvency</b> - – if the Borrower is unable to pay its debts as they fall due with
